<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hunt1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hunt,</orth> subst. 1) chase: <cit><quote>the h. is up,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.2.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 2, 1</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>as if a double h. were heard at once,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.19" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 19</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>escaped the h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 2.3.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 3, 3</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) the game killed in the chase: <cit><quote>we'll go dress our h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 3.6.90" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 6, 90</bibl></cit>.
